      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project or reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some upcoming maintenance and minor repairs to bring it back to its best. It's an honest car at an honest price for those looking for a budget-friendly entry into this model.",
