    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and represents a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a great foundation for a restoration project or a valuable source for parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
