    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and reliable, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. While the car shows minor signs of use, such as light interior wear and a few small stone chips on the exterior, it remains a solid and dependable driver. All electronic components and safety features are fully functional. This is a great opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for daily use without needing immediate repairs.",
